<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Jobs Portal - Home</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="png" sizes="32x32" href="https://i.postimg.cc/mgtpLDsH/favicon-32x32.png">
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        body::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 15px; /* Width of the scrollbar */
          }
          
          body::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #f1f1f1; /* Background color of the scrollbar track */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounding the track */
          }
          
          body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background-color: #1d7756; /* Scrollbar color */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Rounding the scrollbar */
            border: 2px solid #f1f1f1; /* Adds a border for a better effect */
          }
          
          body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background-color: #155b3d; /* Darker color on hover */
          }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            background-color: white;
            color: #338573;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .navbar {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
          }
      
          .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2f7368;
            text-decoration: none;
          }
      
          .navbar .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 20px;
            
          }
      
          .navbar .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
          }
      
          .navbar .post-job-btn {
            background-color: #2f7368;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
          }
      
      
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background:url('image.png') center/cover no-repeat;
            color: black;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            width:auto;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero .cta-button {
            background-color: #338573;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            border: 2px solid white;
        }

        .hero .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #2a6e5d;
        }

        /* Search Section */
        .search-section {
            display: flex;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-top:5rem;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            height:4rem;
            border-color:transparent;
        }

        .search-section input[type="text"] {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 10px;
            border: transparent;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .search-section button {
            background-color: #338573;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size:1.2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            width:7rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .search-section button:hover {
            background-color: #2a6e5d;
        }

        /* Categories Section */
        .categories-section {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .categories-section h2 {
            color: #338573;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .categories-list {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .category-item {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            color: #338573;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            text-align: center;
            width: 140px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .category-item:hover {
            background-color: #e3e3f9;
        }

        /* Job Listings Section */
        .job-listings {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }

        .job-listings h2 {
            color: #338573;
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .job-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-left: 5px solid #338573;
        }

        .job-info {
            max-width: 70%;
        }

        .job-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #338573;
        }

        .job-details {
            color: #555;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .view-details-btn {
            background-color: #338573;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .view-details-btn:hover {
            background-color: #2a6e5d;
        }

        /* Testimonials Section */
.testimonials-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

.testimonials-section h2 {
    color: #338573;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.testimonials-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.testimonial-item {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 300px;
}

/* How It Works Section */
.how-it-works-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
}

.how-it-works-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.step {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 250px;
}

/* Latest News & Articles Section */
.latest-news-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.news-list {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.news-item {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    max-width: 250px;
}

/* FAQ Section */
.faq-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
}

/* Call to Action Section */
.cta-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #338573;
    color: white;
}

.cta-button {
    background-color: #2f7368;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
    margin: 10px;
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #2a6e5d;
}


/* FAQ Section */
.faq-section {
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
    background-color: #ffffff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 800px;
    text-align: left;
}

.faq-section h2 {
    color: #338573;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.faq-container {
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

.faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
}

.faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #338573;
}

.faq-answer {
    display: none; /* Initially hidden */
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    color: #555;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
}

.toggle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #338573;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    display: block; /* Show answer when active */
}

.faq-item.active .toggle {
    transform: rotate(45deg); /* Rotate the plus sign */
}

        /* Footer Section */
        footer {
            background-color: #1d7756;
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #338573;
        }
        .log{
            width:5rem;
            color:white;
            background-color:green;
            border-radius:10px;
            text-align:center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="#" class="logo">JobsPortal</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <% if(admi) { %>
                <a href="/logout" style=color:#2f7368;>Logout</a>
                <a href="/dashboard" style=color:#2f7368;>Dashboard</a>
            <%} else { %>
          <a href="/login" style=color:#2f7368;>Login</a>
          <a href="/signup" style=color:#2f7368;>Signup</a>
          <% } %>
          <a href="/job-posting" class="post-job-btn" style="margin-right:2rem;">Post job</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Find A <span style= color:#338573;>Job</span> That <span style= color:#338573;>Matches</span> Your Passion</h1>
            <p>Hand-picked opportunities to work from home, remotely, freelance, full-time, part-time, contract and internships.</p>

            <!-- Search Section -->
            <div class="search-section">
                <input type="text" placeholder="Search by job title..." />
                <button>Search</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Categories Section -->
    <section class="categories-section">
        <h2>Popular Categories</h2>
        <div class="categories-list">
            <div class="category-item">Technology</div>
            <div class="category-item">Finance</div>
            <div class="category-item">Marketing</div>
            <div class="category-item">Design</div>
            <div class="category-item">Healthcare</div>
            <div class="category-item">Engineering</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Job Listings Section -->
    <section class="job-listings">
        <h2>All Popular Listed Jobs</h2>
        <% for(job of list){ %>
        <div class="job-card">
            <div class="job-info">
                <div class="job-title"><%=job.jobTitle %></div>
                <div class="job-details"><%=job.jobDescription %></div>
                <div class="job-details"><%=job.jobLocation%>| <%=job.salaryRange %> | <%=job.jobType %></div>
            </div>
            <a href="/preview/<%=job._id %>"><button class="view-details-btn">View Details</button></a>
        </div>
        <%}%>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
<section class="testimonials-section">
    <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
    <div class="testimonials-list">
        <div class="testimonial-item">
            <p>"Thanks to JobsPortal, I landed my dream job!"</p>
            <span>- Jane Doe, Software Engineer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
            <p>"The job listings were up-to-date and relevant. Highly recommend!"</p>
            <span>- John Smith, Marketing Manager</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-item">
            <p>"A great platform to connect with employers and find opportunities!"</p>
            <span>- Emily Johnson, Graphic Designer</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq-section">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>What types of jobs can I find on this portal?</h3>
                <span class="toggle">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>You can find various job listings including full-time, part-time, freelance, and internships across multiple industries such as technology, finance, marketing, and more.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>How do I apply for a job?</h3>
                <span class="toggle">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>To apply for a job, simply click on the job listing you are interested in and follow the application instructions provided in the job details.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>Can I post a job listing?</h3>
                <span class="toggle">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>Yes, you can post a job listing by clicking the 'Post Job' button in the navigation bar and filling out the required details in the job posting form.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>Is there a fee to use this job portal?</h3>
                <span class="toggle">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>No, using our job portal is completely free for job seekers. Employers may have fees for premium listings.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">
                <h3>How can I contact support?</h3>
                <span class="toggle">+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                <p>If you need assistance, please visit our Contact Us page, and we will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>© 2022 Jobs Portal. Designed By Wilson Kinyua.</p>
        <p><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </footer>
    <script>
        const faqQuestions = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question');
    
        faqQuestions.forEach(question => {
            question.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const faqItem = question.parentElement;
                faqItem.classList.toggle('active');
            });
        });
    </script>
    
</body>
</html>
